<section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h2>Questions, answered.</h2></div><div class="faq-grid"><article class="faq-card"><h3>Who can attend?</h3><p>The Week is designed for businesses, students, families, researchers and the wider public.</p></article><article class="faq-card"><h3>Will it be accessible?</h3><p>Every event will publish venue access, step-free information and support arrangements before registration opens.</p></article><article class="faq-card"><h3>Can I sponsor or contribute?</h3><p>Yes. Sponsorship and contributor opportunities are available for the whole Week and individual events.</p></article></div></div></section>
